  "name": "Lancelot",
  "title": "Twin Blades of the Round Table",
  "description": "A Knight of the Round Table raised by a faerie known as the Lady of the Lake—that was the original Lancelot. The path this one is walking, and the paths she refuses to follow are not the same as her predecessor's. Her mind is as open as a wide lake, her appearance and expressions ever changing like a water surface that reflects the sky. And still, just like the waters of an inland lake do not ebb and flow with the tide, so does her swordsmanship stay ever unwavering. She withstands every attack and launches her own special move. She bears the title of the strongest like it's nothing, for she is the current Lancelot.",
